data.description: Stately two story tucked in the trees in Piedmont area! Sought after location, convenient to the Union County Bypass, quiet culdesac street in excellent community. 1.18 ACRES of partially wooded and open land. Main floor hosts an open floor plan, spacious kitchen, formal dining room, expansive great room with cozy fireplace. Second floor offers a primary ensuite that is private with dual vanity and garden tub/sep shower, trey ceiling and walk in closet. 3 additional spacious bedrooms provide needed room for a growing family. Deck and covered front porch.  Don't miss this incredible yard with space to add on, build your dream pool, outside living features and more!
